---
title: Gochujang Salmon Poke Bowl with Sesame Sweet Potato and Smacked Cucumber
description: Poke, pronounced poh-kay, is one of Hawaii's most well-known dishes. Poke means 'to slice' or 'cut crosswise into pieces', so we've made a delicious Korean inspired version for our Gochujang Salmon Poke Bowl.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R46_W40_UK_R23292-3_Main_low_2-4e357344.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66a911c46afd9575ba9cb7b3-en-GB.pdf
author: Anushka Magan
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/gochujang-salmon-poke-bowl-66a911c46afd9575ba9cb7b3
course: main course
time required: 35m
nutrition:
  calories: 940 kcal
  fat: 43.6 g
  saturated fat: 12.4 g
